A cyberpunk-style 3D exploded view of a futuristic holographic email interface floating in dark space, with glowing neon blue and magenta wireframe panels separating and hovering at different depths like architectural blueprints. The UI components appear as translucent geometric layers - a navigation sidebar, message list grid, and reading pane - each outlined in electric cyan light trails. Circuit-like patterns pulse through the connections between layers. The scene is set against a deep purple-black void with subtle digital rain particles falling in the background. The overall composition suggests dissection and analysis, with each UI element suspended mid-air as if being examined by an unseen force, casting soft holographic reflections below.
